@FccMiddleware.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5070

GET {{FccMiddleware.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

# Phase 5 suspicious-registration review examples
POST {{FccMiddleware.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/agent/{{deviceId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{portalToken}}

{
  "reason": "Approved replacement after verifying the field swap request."
}

###

POST {{FccMiddleware.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/agent/{{deviceId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{portalToken}}

{
  "reason": "Rejected because the serial number does not match the approved device list."
}

